### Summary
This documentation explains how to deploy and analyze recommendations in personalization campaigns using Amplitude's Profile API, including how to authenticate, query parameters, interpret responses, and integrate the API into digital workflows. It also covers how to analyze recommendation performance through the Performance tab, which shows lift, conversion rates, and statistical significance.

